    760.703587] [ 760.703587] *** DEADLOCK *** Solve this by removing the mutex_lock()/mutex_unlock() calls
    from blk_ia_range_sysfs_show(). (CVE-2022-49406)

Note that Nessus relies on the presence of the package as reported by the vendor.");
